node.text:
You win sum you dim sum.. 

Australia’s lockdowns and cancelled flights are making it hard for myself and a lot of other stranded Aussies overseas to make it home to their families.

Is it the same for other countries too?

A little reminder for anyone who is frustrated with the way things are:

Staying positive doesn’t mean that everything will be ok. It just means that YOU will be ok no matter how things turn out. 

#Staystrong #Bepositive #Mindset #Godsplan

Back to the beginning.. this is where it all started 7 years ago me and @karinaelle used to drive to golds gym every day train here hang out  have a great time. 7 years later and a lot of twists and turns in life along the way it’s nice to come back to the basics here see familiar faces and make some muscles again. Nothing will ever beat our combined workout spirit and friendship in life 😎 #bff4life
